OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer said he left Downing
OL,7,FStreet with "good grace and a smile".
OL,9,FHere is his speech outside Number 10
OL,10,Fin full:
OL,12,F"Thank you very much, and good morning.
OL,14,F"I'm about to visit His Majesty the
OL,15,FKing to offer my resignation and close
OL,16,Fthe book on my time as prime minister.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@dO]tD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
