OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,F"My work is done. In six-and-a-half
OL,7,Fyears, I took our party from a
OL,8,Fhistoric defeat in 2019, changed it so
OL,9,Fit was fit to face the country, and
OL,10,Fwon a landslide general election
OL,11,Fvictory in 2024.
OL,13,F"Since then, it has been the privilege
OL,14,Fof my life to serve you and this great
OL,15,Fcountry as prime minister, and I am
OL,16,Fconfident that Britain is now stronger
OL,17,Fand fairer than it was two years ago.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
