SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784569707
OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,F"Our economy is stronger; our public
OL,7,Fservices are on the up, with the
OL,8,Fbiggest fall in waiting times for 17
OL,9,Fyears; children are being lifted out
OL,10,Fof poverty every single day;
OL,11,Fimmigration is down significantly; our
OL,12,Fdefence and security are on a far
OL,13,Fstronger footing and our international
OL,14,Freputation is greatly advanced.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784569707
OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,F"Yet the thing I will always take away
OL,7,Fwith me ` the most humbling aspect of
OL,8,Fthis job ` is the front-row seat you
OL,9,Fget to witness the greatest things of
OL,10,Fthis country in action, to see every
OL,11,Fday immeasurable acts of resolve,
OL,12,Fgrit, decency, and compassion from
OL,13,Fpeople who serve our country, whether
OL,14,Fthat's in their regimental colours,
OL,15,FNHS scrubs, or simply the millions of
OL,16,Fpeople in their communities who
OL,17,Fvolunteer their time and their effort
OL,18,Fto the ground beneath their feet.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
