OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784569707
OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,F"We face a world now where our enemies
OL,7,Fwill stop at nothing to divide us
OL,8,Fbecause of our values, our freedom,
OL,9,Four decency, and frankly, because of
OL,10,Four unflinching resolve towards the
OL,11,Fbrave people of Ukraine.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
