CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784569707
OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,F"And so, under this attack, it is
OL,7,Fvital that we remember the greatness
OL,8,Fof the Britain all around us. That
OL,9,Fwhile we debate how to fix our
OL,10,Fproblems, there is something we
OL,11,Finherit from our country and our
OL,12,Fcharacter that can give us confidence
OL,13,Fthat we can change our country for the
OL,14,Fbetter, that we can create a Britain
OL,15,Fwhere every child can go as far as
OL,16,Ftheir talent will take them, and we
OL,17,Fcan unite different people under our
OL,18,Fcommon flag if we don't succumb to
OL,19,Fthat division.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
