OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"So, as I now pass the baton to Andy
OL,12,FBurnham, I wish him every success. He
OL,13,Fhas my full support.
OL,15,F"And finally, I want to thank once
OL,16,Fagain my family, Vic, and our
OL,17,Fchildren, my team, all the staff here
OL,18,Fand across the Labour Party, everyone
OL,19,Fat Number 10, and across the civil
OL,20,Fservice, and everyone who has
OL,21,Fsupported our efforts along the way.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
