PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784569707
OL,3,C'I leave with good grace and a smile':
OL,4,CStarmer's final speech in full
OL,6,F"For all the focus on individuals,
OL,7,Fpolitics will always be a team sport,
OL,8,Fand the changes we've delivered for
OL,9,Four country and our party belong to
OL,10,Feveryone who has fought for them.
OL,12,F"I thank them again today, and I thank
OL,13,Fthe British people for the opportunity
OL,14,Fto serve. I go with good grace. I go
OL,15,Fwith a smile, and I go proud of
OL,16,Feverything that we have achieved.
OL,18,F"Thank you very much."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
